column5: Our own OFC'r Nita put this on Facebook, and I had to share.  I have to do this.  This looks so cool and I wonder where it is.  Anyone else want to join me

Good use of a freestyle skiing practice ramp! Use to be one at Kelso in Milton.  Guess I should add some "lip" to the bottom of my 173 footer, that I built this summer for Jen..and well yes all us other kids!
